hadiths[15]{hadithnumber,text}:
1401,"Hazrat Amr bin al-Aas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey Quran mein pandarah sajdey padhaaey , un mein se teen Juze mufassal (aakhiri manzil) mein (Sura Najm , Sura الانشقاق, aur Sura العلق mein) aur do sura hajj mein hain. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ke wastey se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se giyara sajdey manqul hain, albatta iski sanad kamzor hai."
1402,Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya Sura Haj mein do sajdey hain? aapney farmaya : '' haan ! aur jo ye na karna chahey wo unki tilawat hi na karey.''
1403,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madina tashrif laney ke baad Juz (hissa) mufassal mein kisi maqam par sajda nahin kiya.
1404,"Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney Sura Najm ki tilawat ki, magar aapney us mein sajda nahin kiya."
1405,Khaarija bin Zaid bin Sabit apney walid se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani riwayat kartey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Zaid Imam they aur unhoney sajda nahin kiya.
1406,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sura Najm ki tilawat ki aur us mein sajda kiya aur haazirin mein se sab ne sajda kiya, siwaye eik aadmi ke . usney kankariyon ki ya mitti ki eik mutthi li aur apney chehrey ki taraf uthai aur kaha : mujhey yehi kafi hai. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke baad mein maine usey dekha ke haalate kufr mein qatl kar diya gaya."
1407,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath sura (إذا السماء انشقت) aur) َاقْرَأْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ الَّذِي خَلَقَ ( mein sajdey kiye. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Fateh khaibar ke mauqe par san chhe hijrii mein musalman huey hain. aur ye sajdey karna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka aakhiri amal hai.
1408,"Abu-Raafe (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke maine Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Isha ki Namaz padhi , unhoney Namaz mein sura ( إِذَا السَّمَاءُ انْشَقَّتْ ( tilawat ki aur sajda bhi kiya. maine puchha ke ye kaisa sajda hai? unhoney kaha : maine Hazrat Abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey ye sajda kiya hai. aur main isey nahin chhodun ga yahan tak ke aap se ja miloon."
1409,"Ikrima se riwayat hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke sura (ص) ka sajda waajibi sajdon mein se nahin hai, jabke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap is mein sajda kartey they."
1410,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne member par sura (ص) ki tilawat ki . jab sajdey ki aayat par pahunchey to aap member se nichey tashrif laye aur sajda kiya aur aap ke sath logon ne bhi sajda kiya. phir eik doosra mauqa aaya aur aapney usi ki tilawat farmaai . jab aap sajdey ki aayat par pahunchey to log sajdey ke liye tayyar ho gaey . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye eik Nabi (Hazrat Dawud Alahissalaam) ki tauba ka zikr hai lekin maine tumhen dekha hai ke tum sajda karna chahtey ho.'' chunanche aap utrey aur sajda kiya aur logon ne bhi sajda kiya."
1411,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke mauqe par sajdey ki aayat tilawat farmaai to sab logon ne sajda kiya. un mein se kuch sawaariyon par Sawar they aur kuch zameen par sajda kerney waley they. sawar logon ne apney apney haath par sajda kiya.
1412,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham par koi surat tilawat farmatey . ... ibne-Numair ne kaha : Namaz ke alawa , aam haalat mein , phir dono ka bayan hai. ... ke aap sajda kartey aur ham bhi aap ke sath sajda kartey , yahan tak ke ham mein se baaz ko peshani rakhney ke liye jagah na milti thi."
1413,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ham par Quran padha kartey they. jab sajdey ki aayat se guzartey to (الله اكبر) kehtey aur sajdey mein chaley jatey aur ham bhi aap ke sath sajda kartey. Janab Abdur-Razzaaq ne bayan kiya ke Imam Sauri ko ye hadees bahut pasand thi. Imam Abu-Dawud ne bayan kiya. ... kyonkey is mein takbir ka zikr hai.
1414,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko sajda Quran mein ye dua takraar se padha (dohraaya) kartey they : ( سَجَدَ وَجْهِي لِلَّذِي خَلَقَهُ وَشَقَّ سَمْعَهُ وَ بَصَرَهُ بِحَوْلِهِ وَ قُوَّتِهِ ) ''mera chehra us zaat ke liye sajda rez hai jisney isko paida kiya aur apni taqat aur quwwat se uskey kaan aur aankh banaey.''
1415,"Abu-Tameema Hujaimi kehtey hain ke jab ham qafley walon ke sath Madina aaye to main Namaze-Fajr ke baad waaz kiya karta tha aur is mein sajda tilawat kiya karta tha. isliye Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne mujh ko roka , teen baar . magar main na rukaa . phir palat kar unhoney kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke peechhey aur Hazrat abu-Bakar , Hazrat umr aur Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ke sath namaazen padhi hain. ye hazraat sajda na kartey they, yahan tak ke Suraj tulu ho jata."
